        "description": "Avatar Recording is designed to facilitate the seamless recording and export of Meta avatars.\n\nUsers can effortlessly record their avatars within the immersive confines of virtual reality or in passthrough mode. Compatible with Meta Quest Pro, Quest 2, and Quest 3.\n\nCapture the subtle nuances of expression with precision using Avatar Recording's blend shape functionality. From delicate smiles to intricate gestures, every facet of an avatar's demeanor is faithfully preserved, enabling animations that resonate with authenticity.\n\nVoice recording allows users to synchronize recorded audio with their animations. Whether narrating a story, delivering a presentation, or engaging in virtual conversation. Elevate realism with eye tracking, supported on Meta Quest Pro. \n\nSimplify the sharing process with seamless export to GLB format. With just a few taps, users can share their creations across platforms or integrate them seamlessly into other projects.\n",
